author: Kim Villalobos
text:
This author has seen enough!

I speak of this season's diamond, Lt. Gov. of Wisconsin, @TheOtherMandela. 

A  believer of opportunity for all! He does more than just sparkle; he rises and stands ready against the greatest of challenges. 

Your move, @RonJohnsonWI
